===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# The act or process of [[punish]]ing, imposing and/or applying a [[sanction]].
# A [[penalty]] to punish wrongdoing, especially for [[crime]].
# A [[suffering]] by [[pain]] or [[loss]] imposed as [[retribution]]
# {{figurative}} Any [[treatment]] or experience so [[harsh]] it feels like being punished
#:''The drunk champions team got a terrible '''punishment''': a 0-10 loss, as shamefull as the bare-butt paddling they got afterward

